		</Group>
		<RichText x="738" y="223" width="397" height="56" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">歌裴莉娅和科培琉司依次进行一次划击，均造成<span color="#bfffdf">对应元素</span><span>的</span><span color="#edffbf">60%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="1410" y="223" width="399" height="56" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">科培琉司旋转魔杖在前方生成大块冰簇，造成<span color="#99ffff">80%</span><span>伤害，随后冰簇消散。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="1410" y="895" width="424" height="114" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">告别科培琉司后，歌裴莉娅进行一次气暴，造成<span color="#7fffd7">90%</span><span>伤害同时暴露</span><span textDecoration="underline" color="#b299ff">荒性核心</span><span>，持续至组曲结束，随后便等待科培琉司回归。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="671" width="1005" height="114" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">歌裴莉娅和科培琉司开始进行表演，主角为歌裴莉娅，场地内形成顺时针游动的3个风之心，其不断牵引玩家造成<span color="#7fffd7">15%</span><span>伤害，其可被科培琉司的冰刃染色，染冰后造成</span><span color="#7fffd7">25%</span><span>+</span><span color="#99ffff">25%</span><span>伤害。<br/>该技能分三个阶段：送别，独奏，回归，持续3个</span><span textDecoration="underline">循环</span><span>、8/3个</span><span textDecoration="underline">回合</span><span>。每回合开始时，其将获得25%全抗性加成。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/冰风组曲%B7歌裴莉娅的葬送.assets/Image_14.png')" x="720" y="138">
		</BitmapImage>
