		</BitmapImage>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/冰风组曲%B7歌裴莉娅的葬送.assets/Image_21.png')" x="1392" y="1033">
		</BitmapImage>
		<RichText x="738" y="447" width="424" height="85" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">科培琉司顺时针溜冰一圈，造成<span color="#99ffff">70%</span><span>伤害，其行动轨迹留下冰块，将以逆时针顺序依次引爆，造成</span><span color="#99ffff">80%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="1410" y="447" width="408" height="56" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">科培琉司旋转魔杖施放出若干个冰锥，每个造成<span color="#99ffff">75%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="1119" width="439" height="85" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">科培琉司在场地外挥出2刀冰刃，均造成<span color="#99ffff">100%</span><span>伤害，随后滑冰准备回归，冰刃会将其划过的风之心染色。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="1410" y="1119" width="442" height="172" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">科培琉司在场地高速滑冰，溅射的冰碎持续造成<span color="#99ffff">40%</span><span>伤害，同时在场地中央进行旋舞，进行4段普通攻击，均造成</span><span color="#7fffd7">92%</span><span>伤害，最后产生2次气暴，造成</span><span color="#7fffd7">90%</span><span>伤害并推开玩家，可被削弱 (芒削效果：造成</span><span color="#7fffd7">60%</span><span>伤害且推力消失)。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="899" y="62" fontFamily="造字工房悦圆 G0v1 常规体" fontSize="24" fontStyle="normal" fontWeight="normal" color="#268e62" width="207" height="28" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="1">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="造字工房悦圆 G0v1 常规体" fontSize="24" color="#268e62">制图@Csxylic米游社</p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="895" width="430" height="114" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">歌裴莉娅将科培琉司送出，送出时将进行辞离颂舞：均进行多段划击，均造成<span color="#bfffdf">对应元素</span><span>的</span><span color="#ebffbf">60%,30%</span><span>伤害；科培琉司滑冰移走，造成2段</span><span color="#99ffff">80%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/冰风组曲%B7歌裴莉娅的葬送.assets/Image_22.png')" x="719" y="810">
		</BitmapImage>
