		<RichText x="66" y="1192" width="442" height="97" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.7490196078431373">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="16" fontWeight="bold" color="#b299ff">荒性核心<span color="#ffffff">：累计受到3次</span><span color="#ffe599">芒性攻击</span><span color="#ffffff">方可打断瘫痪组曲，每次</span><span color="#ffe599">芒性攻击</span><span color="#ffffff">方可削弱歌裴莉娅在本回合中的技能</span><span color="#7fffd7">风葬回旋-气暴</span><span color="#ffffff">下的风场推力，并使其伤害倍率下降</span><span color="#ff9999">50%</span><span color="#ffffff">，移除该回合的抗性提升。<br/>回合：完整进行独奏、回归、送别三个阶段称为一个回合。<br/>循环：完整进行送别、独奏、回归三个阶段称为一个循环。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
